Practical 3
Program 1
Implement a JS program which demonstrates the use of JavaScript functions and function closure.
Code:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
        <title>JavaScript Closure Example </title>
</head>
<body>
    <h3>JavaScript Function Flow With Closure</h3>
    <button onclick="countClick()">Click Me</button>
    <script>
     function createCounter(){
        let count = 0;
        return function () {
            count++;
            alert("Button clicked" + count + "times")  };  }
     let countClick = createCounter();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
